    "body": "It appears that all the EL clients have resolved this issue with `eth_feeHistory`. Going forward, yes, we need to be vigilant that clients behave the same before going live. We've done some work since this issue was posted to be able to catch issues early, on all clients, automatically. This is done by running `rpc-compat` simulator in hive: https://github.com/ethereum/hive/tree/master/simulators/ethereum/rpc-compat",
